506
00:34:33,508 --> 00:34:34,001
De l'eau.

507
00:34:34,688 --> 00:34:35,262
Oui.

508
00:34:38,405 --> 00:34:39,623
Je regardais tes coupures de presse.

509
00:34:40,537 --> 00:34:42,293
